entries.meaning: (uncountable) The game of tag, or it, in which the player attempting to catch the others is called "he".
The player who chases and attempts to catch the others in this game.

examples: Is your cat a he or a she?

entries.meaning: The name of the fifth letter of many Semitic alphabets (Phoenician, Aramaic, Hebrew, Syriac, Arabic and others).
examples: The same number in the Hebrew mysteries and Cabalistical accounts was the character of Generation; declared by the Letter He, the fifth in their Alphabet.

entries.meaning: The name of the first letter of the Old South Arabian abjad.
